#### Creating your first bot

1. Open the **Bot Framework Emulator Composer**
2. Click on **New** button
    ![](images/3.jpg)
3. Check the **Create from template** option, select **Echo Bot** and click on **Next**
    ![](images/4.jpg)
4. Set **ComposerDemo** as name then click on Next
   ![](images/5.jpg)
5. In the bot designer click on **Add +** button and select **Add new trigger on ComposerDemo**
    ![](images/6.jpg)
6. Now fill the next field with the following:
- **What is the name of this trigger (LUIS)**
  - CollectInformation
- **Trigger Phrases**
  - Save my information
  - information
  - please collection my information
7. Add a new question by clicking in the **+** button then select **Ask a question** and **Text**
    ![](images/7.jpg)